In [9]:
annual_flights = {}
annual_flights_scheduled = {}
passengers = {}
seats = {}
freight = {}
mail = {}
payload = {}
for year in years:
    annual_flights[year] = sum(data[data.YEAR == year].DEPARTURES_PERFORMED)
    annual_flights_scheduled[year] = sum(data[data.YEAR == year].DEPARTURES_SCHEDULED)
    passengers[year] = sum(data[data.YEAR == year].PASSENGERS)
    seats[year] = sum(data[data.YEAR == year].SEATS)
    freight[year] = sum(data[data.YEAR == year].FREIGHT)
    mail[year] = sum(data[data.YEAR == year].MAIL)
    payload[year] = sum(data[data.YEAR == year].PAYLOAD)

In [11]:
monthly_flights = {}
for year in years:
    for month in range(1,10):
        monthly_flights[str(year)+'_0'+str(month)] = sum(data[(data.YEAR==year)&(data.MONTH==month)].DEPARTURES_PERFORMED)
    for month in range(10,13):
        monthly_flights[str(year)+'_'+str(month)] = sum(data[(data.YEAR==year)&(data.MONTH==month)].DEPARTURES_PERFORMED)

visited_countries = {}
visiting_country = {}
#most_visited = {}
i=0
for year in years:
    visited = {}
    visitor = {}
    for country in data[data.YEAR == year].DEST_COUNTRY_NAME:
        if country != 'United States':# and country != 'Canada' and country != 'Mexico':
            visited[country] = visited.get(country, 0)\
            +data.at[i,'DEPARTURES_PERFORMED']
        if country == 'United States':
            guest = data.at[i, 'ORIGIN_COUNTRY_NAME']
            visitor[guest] = visitor.get(guest, 0)\
            +data.at[i,'DEPARTURES_PERFORMED']
        i += 1
    visited_countries[year] = visited
    visiting_country[year] = visitor

nodes = []
links = []
cities = []
for line in range(len((data[data.YEAR==1990]))):
#for line in range(100):
    city_country_orig = data[(data.YEAR==1990)].at[line, 'ORIGIN_CITY_NAME']
    loc1 = str.find(city_country_orig, ',')
#    city = city_country[:loc]
#    country = city_country[loc+2:]
    cit1 = (city_country_orig[:loc1], city_country_orig[loc1+2:])
    #index1 = re.search(cities, cit1)
    if cit1 not in cities:
        cities.append(cit1)
        nodes.append({'name':city_country_orig[:loc1], 'group':city_country_orig[loc1+2:]})
    city_country_dest = data[(data.YEAR==1990)].at[line, 'DEST_CITY_NAME']
    loc2 = str.find(city_country_dest, ',')
    cit2 = (city_country_dest[:loc2], city_country_dest[loc2+2:])
    #index2 = str.find(cities, cit2)
    if cit2 not in cities:
        cities.append(cit2)
        nodes.append({'name':city_country_dest[:loc2], 'group':city_country_dest[loc2+2:]})
    
    links.append({'source': nodes.index({'name':city_country_orig[:loc1], 'group':city_country_orig[loc1+2:]})\
                  , 'target': nodes.index({'name':city_country_dest[:loc2], 'group':city_country_dest[loc2+2:]})})
#    print(cities)
#     graph
#     print(data[data.YEAR==1990].at[line, 'ORIGIN_CITY_NAME'])
# print(nodes)
# print(links)
dat['nodes'] = nodes
dat['links'] = links
